import { Divider } from "@material-ui/core"
import { TextField } from "@material-ui/core"
import { Button } from "@material-ui/core"

const MainForm = ({text, setText, day , setDay}) => {
    return (
        <>
            <Divider />
                <form>
                    <TextField id="standard-basic" label="Užduotis" />
                    <Button
                        variant="contained"
                        color="primary"
                    >Pridėti
                    </Button>
                </form>
            <Divider />
        </>
    )
}

export default MainForm
